query:
UPDATE 
                capture_config 
            SET 
                last_server_ping = now(), 
                error = $1 
            WHERE 
                workspace_id = $2 AND 
                path = $3 AND 
                is_flow = $4 AND 
                trigger_kind = 'sqs' AND 
                server_id = $5 AND 
                last_client_ping > NOW() - INTERVAL '10 seconds' 
            RETURNING 1
